<div class="grouping">
    <div class="group">
        <a name="quantastor-storage-server" />
        <h2 style="margin-top: 1px">QuantaStor Storage Server</h2>
        <p>QuantaStor Storage Servers combine the QuantaStor OS from OS Nexus with SoftLayer 12 or 24 drive mass storage
            servers, bringing you a private SAN or NAS appliance for more storage with higher security, control and
            scalability. Ideal for applications including virtual servers and desktops, video production and web and
            application servers, QuantaStor is the most comprehensive mass storage solution, with features including
            snapshots, compression, thin-provisioning and remote-replication.</p>
        <span class="standardText">Learn more about:</span><br />
        <div class="moreInfoLinkSet noTopMargin">
            <div class="left-element headingLink"><a href="/services/storagelayer/quantastor-servers">QuantaStor Storage Servers</a></div>
            <a href="/services/storagelayer/quantastor-servers" class="read-more-red-circle-arrow"></a>
        </div>

    </div>
    <div class="group">
        <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" summary="Bandwidth" class="price2" style="margin: 1px; padding: 0;">
            <tr>
                <th class="highlight">Configuration</th>
                <th class="highlight" style="text-align: right;">Monthly</th>
            </tr>
            <tr class="alternate">
                <td style="font-size: 11px">Up to 12 HDDs</td>
                <td class="cost" style="font-size: 11px">(starting at) $919.00</td>
            </tr>
