<div class="grouping">
    <div class="group">
        <a name="iscsi-storage-replication-and-snapshots" />
        <h2 style="margin-top: 1px">iSCSI Storage, Replication and Snapshots</h2>
        <p>iSCSI Storage allows users to mount remote, enterprise-grade, SAN storage disks as though they were attached locally. It is scalable, easily provisioned, and outperforms internal disks, providing a low-cost alternative to traditional fiber-channel storage solutions. Replications of iSCSI volumes can be sent to another SoftLayer data center in the U.S., Asia, or Europe for painless disaster recovery. Point-in-time snapshots of iSCSI volumes can be scheduled, stored locally or remotely, and later accessed for data recovery or current data comparison.</p>
    </div>
